The resistance of [$cucumber#Plant*] accession 27028930 to [$MYSV#Virus*] is temperature dependent and intermediate; [$melon#Plant*] isolate ([$MYSV-S#Virus*]) inoculation resulted in no systemic infection of resistant [$cucumber plants#Plant*] at low temperature (20 degrees C).
The [$melon#Plant*] accession JP 138332 exhibits high resistance to [$CCYV#Virus*].
